{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_288b23549ffeOcHU4Vmxxc6Hjq","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d775594fa001oOmg4qOuZ8Br4p","parts":[{"id":"prt_d77559c04001oU68HFl5jY49MB","messageID":"msg_d775594fa001oOmg4qOuZ8Br4p","sessionID":"ses_288b23549ffeOcHU4Vmxxc6Hjq","type":"text","text":"## 仓库配置完成报告\n\n### 仓库信息\n- **仓库名称**: armi (Advanced Reactor Modeling Interface)\n- **版本**: 0.7.0\n- **Python 版本**: 3.11.2\n\n### 已完成的关键步骤\n\n#### 1. 环境准备\n```bash\napt-get update && apt-get install -y python3-pip python3-venv\npython3 -m venv /workspace/venv\npip install -U pip\n```\n\n#### 2. 依赖安装\n```bash\npip install -e .                    # 安装主包及核心依赖\npip install -e \".[test]\"            # 安装测试依赖\n```\n\n**安装的主要依赖包**:\n- numpy, scipy, matplotlib, h5py\n- pytest, pytest-cov, pytest-xdist\n- ruff (代码检查工具)\n- sympy, ruamel.yaml, voluptuous 等\n\n#### 3. 验证测试\n\n| 测试模块 | 通过数 | 跳过数 | 状态 |\n|---------|-------|-------|------|\n| armi/tests/ | 86 | 16 (MPI) | ✅ |\n| armi/materials/tests/ | 519 | 0 | ✅ |\n| armi/utils/tests/ | 324 | 1 | ✅ |\n| armi/reactor/tests/ | 78 | 0 | ✅ |\n| armi/bookkeeping/tests/ | 21 | 0 | ✅ |\n| armi/settings/tests/ | 48 | 0 | ✅ |\n| armi/nucDirectory/tests/ | 51 | 0 | ✅ |\n| armi/physics/neutronics/tests/ | 72 | 0 | ✅ |\n| armi/nuclearDataIO/tests/ | 47 | 0 | ✅ |\n| **综合测试** | **2597** | **17 (MPI)** | ✅ |\n\n#### 4. 代码质量检查\n```bash\nruff check armi/__init__.py armi/plugins.py armi/context.py\n# All checks passed!\n```\n\n### 最终状态\n- ✅ 虚拟环境创建成功 (`/workspace/venv`)\n- ✅ ARMI 0.7.0 安装成功\n- ✅ CLI 命令 `armi` 可用\n- ✅ 核心模块导入正常\n- ✅ 2597 个测试通过\n- ✅ 17 个 MPI 相关测试跳过（需要 MPI 环境）\n- ✅ 代码检查通过\n\n### 无失败项\n\n**环境配置完成，所有验证通过。**","time":{"start":1775823602678,"end":1775823602678}}]}
