 | 0 | ✅ |\n| **综合测试** | **2597** | **17 (MPI)** | ✅ |\n\n#### 4. 代码质量检查\n```bash\nruff check armi/__init__.py armi/plugins.py armi/context.py\n# All checks passed!\n```\n\n### 最终状态\n- ✅ 虚拟环境创建成功 (`/workspace/venv`)\n- ✅ ARMI 0.7.0 安装成功\n- ✅ CLI 命令 `armi` 可用\n- ✅ 核心模块导入正常\n- ✅ 2597 个测试通过\n- ✅ 17 个 MPI 相关测试跳过（需要 MPI 环境）\n- ✅ 代码检查通过\n\n### 无失败项\n\n**环境配置完成，所有验证通过。**","time":{"start":1775823602678,"end":1775823602678},"id":"prt_d77559c04001oU68HFl5jY49MB","sessionID":"ses_288b23549ffeOcHU4Vmxxc6Hjq","messageID":"msg_d775594fa001oOmg4qOuZ8Br4p"},{"reason":"stop","snapshot":"0082fb34bfa107cb33227a1c406f750a9b95496b","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":60216,"input":59638,"output":578,"reasoning":12,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0,"id":"prt_d7755c3f8001HkJYcmjR7IDjwe","sessionID":"ses_288b23549ffeOcHU4Vmxxc6Hjq","messageID":"msg_d775594fa001oOmg4qOuZ8Br4p"}]}}
